data.description: EXCELLENT INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY to own a fully occupied mixed use property in Atlantic city. This property consists of 1 retail outlet and 4 residential units, totaling 5 income producing units.  The Store is located on the ground floor. First floor consists of 1 three-bedroom apartment with 2 baths and 1 studio with a full bath. Second floor has 2 two-bedroom apartments with 2 full baths.  Store is for a 5-year lease and all the residential units are on yearly lease. Generating $7,000 rent per month.  Tenants pay all utilities. Current owner has expanded the building to a 4 units rental place.
